    <avalancheActivity>
      <highlights>Wind slabs and wet snow represent the main danger.</highlights>
      <comment>In particular on steep slopes individual small to medium-sized slab avalanches are possible above approximately 1400 m. &lt;br/> In the vicinity of peaks a dangerous avalanche situation will be encountered in some localities. The more recent wind slabs and can be released easily. &lt;br/> Avalanches can penetrate down to the ground and reach medium size in some cases.</comment>
